title: Great FSU visit for Ocean Lakes RB
text: "Great" FSU visit for 2017 R100 RB Laborn Adam Friedman Rivals.com Football Recruiting Florida State's game against Miami brought dozens of highly rated prospects to Tallahassee. Among them was 2017 Rivals100 running back Khalan Laborn . The Virginia Beach (Va.) Ocean Lakes standout has the Seminoles very high on his list and the visit seemed to solidify Florida State's standing with Laborn. ... More ... To continue reading this article you must be a member.
